Get the latest uploads of Library Genesis.

libgen_new_uploads.Rd

This function gets the latest uploads of Library Genesis in specified time period.

libgen_new_uploads(timefirst, timelast = Sys.Date(), mode = "last",
  only_id = FALSE, full_fields = FALSE, fields = c(), count = 1000,
  first = 1)

Arguments

timefirst

the beginning time of query, in the format of 'YYYY-MM-DD'.
timelast

the ending time of query, in the format of 'YYYY-MM-DD', defaults to current day.
mode

last to return last uploaded results, modified to return last modified results. Defaults to last.
only_id

whether returns only id fields so that results can be passed to get_by_ID function. Defaults to FALSE.
full_fields

whether returns with full fields (TRUE) or selected fields (FALSE).
fields

Optional, user specified vector of fields to return.
count

number of items to return, defaults to 1000.
first

the first row to return, defaults to 1.

Value

A data frame with results or a vector of character if only_id==TRUE.
